p.text: I, (name) of (address) do swear that (if the oath is taken in relation to proceedings commenced or proposed to be commenced under the Mutual Recognition Act 1992 of the Commonwealth or under the Trans Tasman Mutual Recognition Act 1997 of the Commonwealth, add if I am enrolled as a legal practitioner by the Supreme Court of New South Wales) I will truly and honestly conduct myself in the practice of a legal practitioner of the Supreme Court of New South Wales and I shall faithfully serve as such in the administration of the laws and the usages of that State according to the best of my knowledge, skill and ability.
I, (name) of (address), certify that I duly administered the above oath on (date)
